g", "text": "Love this! Thank you!", "author": "@Armchair-Investor", "like_count": 0, "published_at": "2023-04-08T20:09:46Z", "parent_id": null, "video_id": "Z9SFLO1lTbc"}, {"id": "Ugx4oY-Efh2VJa3f7Th4AaABAg", "text": "\ud83e\udd14Thinking of moving to or selling your home in Irvine California?\ud83c\udf34\r\n\ud83d\udcf1Call or text:  949-285-1207\r\n\ud83d\udce7Email:  info@livinginirvinecalifornia.com\r\n\ud83d\udcc5Zoom:  http://bit.ly/3ZeNnEa\r\n Full Channel: \ud83d\udc49\ud83d\udc49\ud83d\udc49: https://bit.ly/3NXecX3", "author": "@LivinginIrvineCalifornia", "like_count": 0, "published_at": "2023-02-03T02:46:43Z", "parent_id": null, "video_id": "uBqgKZY6gL0"}, {"id": "UgyMknfXSZopc6ZCzrl4AaABAg", "text": "Hello There!\n\nI have analyzed your YouTube channel and found out some problems, do You want to talk it for a while?", "author": "@seospecialistbyuzzal", "like_count": 0, "published_at": "2026-03-05T19:27:39Z", "parent_id": null, "video_id": "MUOvDKDwar4"}, {"id": "UgzaKu7hTVg3RKcqHcJ4AaABAg", "text": "freaky", "author": "@55AZ55", "like_count": 0, "published_at": "2026-01-21T11:46:21Z", "parent_id": null, "video_id": "MUOvDKDwar4"}]', 0.5, '{"sources": {"zori_csv": false, "overpass_grocery": true, "overpass_night_activity": false, "overpass_noise": true, "irvine_crime": false, "irvine_crime_source": "missing:missing_api_key", "crime_api": false, "crime_api_source": "missing:missing_api_key", "youtube_video": true, "commute_minutes": null, "viirs_night_activity": false, "night_activity_source": "cached"}}');
